# Sprint Relay Webhook Testing

## Checklist:
- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:3000
- [ ] Open 'Lark Webhook Settings' modal
- [ ] Scroll to 'Test Lark Connection' section
- [ ] Verify dropdowns:
    - [ ] Current Sprint
    - [ ] Next Sprint (Target)
    - [ ] Task Status
    - [ ] Task Sprint Goal
- [ ] Verify sprint labels ('Sprint 8') vs values ('8')
- [ ] Perform selection:
    - [ ] Select '8' for Current Sprint
    - [ ] Select '9' for Next Sprint
    - [ ] Select 'Testing' for Task Status
    - [ ] Select '9' for Task Sprint Goal
- [ ] Click 'Run Test'
- [ ] Verify JSON output:
    - [ ] 'currentSprint' is "8"
    - [ ] 'nextSprint' is "9"
    - [ ] 'todos[0].status' is "Testing"
    - [ ] 'todos[0].sprintGoal' is "9"
- [ ] Take a screenshot
